WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.389
Hey, good morning, family. Praise the

00:00:02.399 --> 00:00:04.789
Lord. Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:04.799 --> 00:00:07.349
Well, we see all this stuff in the news.

00:00:07.359 --> 00:00:11.749
Yesterday was a wow, wasn't it? With

00:00:11.759 --> 00:00:15.190
the earthquake in Alaska, the major

00:00:15.200 --> 00:00:17.990
earthquake in Alaska, then we had

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.390
the attack on Damascus. And

00:00:22.400 --> 00:00:23.830
