00:00:58.640 --> 00:01:01.910
Israel is already attacking Syria. What

00:01:01.920 --> 00:01:05.350
will be the outcome concerning this?

00:01:05.360 --> 00:01:07.429
I believe though there is a

00:01:07.439 --> 00:01:10.390
