00:02:05.119 --> 00:02:06.789
just know I saw it coming, and I saw

00:02:06.799 --> 00:02:08.869
Damascus becoming what the Bible calls a

00:02:08.879 --> 00:02:11.750
ruinous heap. So that was

00:02:11.760 --> 00:02:14.150
part of what we saw yesterday. So I

00:02:14.160 --> 00:02:15.910
know there'll be an outcry if this keeps

00:02:15.920 --> 00:02:18.790
