00:02:49.360 --> 00:02:51.990
raising up leaders of prayer warriors in

00:02:51.990 --> 00:02:52.000
these

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:54.470
end times to go and pray on

00:02:54.480 --> 00:02:56.790
YouTube. A million-person men and women prayer

00:02:56.800 --> 00:02:59.110
army is what I'm called to

00:02:59.120 --> 00:03:01.480
