00:03:10.480 --> 00:03:12.149
one of you that are serious about

00:03:12.159 --> 00:03:14.470
prayer. Welcome. Thank you for joining

00:03:14.480 --> 00:03:16.869
us. We take prayer very seriously in our

00:03:16.879 --> 00:03:18.710
